##  # ---------- Calibration anchors ----------
##  # Fezolinetant 45 mg (SKYLIGHT 1/2) : HF freq -63 to -64% at wk 12 vs -35% placebo
##  # Fezolinetant 30 mg (SKYLIGHT 1/2) : HF freq -60% at wk 12
##  # Elinzanetant 120 mg (OASIS 1/2)   : HF freq -74 to -84% at wk 12
##  # Oral/transdermal E2 (WHI/PEPI)    : HF freq -75 to -90% (most efficacious)
##  # Paroxetine 7.5 mg (Stearns 2003)  : HF freq -55 to -65% vs -35% placebo
##  # Venlafaxine 75 mg (Loprinzi 2000) : HF freq -55% vs -15% placebo
